name: Red Pill Expo 2021 portrait Chris, Drew & Travis by Ulysses XYZ
description: Unique digital portrait of Chris Taylor, Drew Ortwein and Travis hand-drawn by Ulysses Penfield (uly.xyz) and minted by Volition Labs (volitionlabs.io) on 11/07/2021, the last day of Red Pill Expo 2021 and the 90th birthday of G Edward Griffin.
